data.description: Offering $5,000 in Buyer Incentives! Welcome to this charming and spacious home located in the beautiful Sugar Creek community with seasonal views of the Big Sugar Golf Course and up the street from the clubhouse. The main floor features the master suite with a large walk-in closet, guest bedroom and bathroom, walk-in pantry, mudroom, laundry, office, spacious kitchen with custom-made cabinetry, formal dining, breakfast room, and living room. The basement features two bedrooms, a bathroom, a kitchenette/wet bar with a dining or sitting area, a family room with surround sound, an extensive craft room, and two additional heated and cooled large storage closets. Don’t miss the upper and lower decks overlooking the golf course and gorgeous dogwoods in the springtime. The basement can be used as a separate living area with a private lower-level entrance. Don't forget, sellers offering $5,000 in Buyer Incentives for golf course membership, paint, carpet, or more…. Buyers’ Choice! Zoned for Rogers School District.
